Liza Minnelli daghter of Judy Garland and Vincente Minnelli, motion picture director, was married here last evening to Peter Woolnough Allen, a song writer and singer. He is the son of Mr. and Mrs. Woolnough Allen of Sydney, Australia. View Full Article in Timesmachine Â»
